name: Jefferson Splash 4
description:
This is a very unique style of painting created by Ashton Jefferson. This Style is a perfect example of controlled chaos, Ashton actually throws the paint onto the canvas in such a way that it creates hidden images. If you look at the painting it looks as if it's just a abstract with paint splashed around the canvas, but as you back away or look at it from a angle you actually see images hidden inside of the painting that create a scene.
24in x 48in acrylic on canvas
( This is the frist time this painting have ever been available online)
